{
  "texts": [
    "To assess overall impacts, we employ a dynamic difference-in-differences specification that compares the monthly outcomes of adopters and non-adopters before and after the introduction of AI chatbots:",
    "where λ 2m are month fixed effects that control for seasonality in labor market outcomes.",
    "The parameters of interest, β τ, capture the differential changes in labor market outcomes for adopters, indexed to November 2022, the release of ChatGPT.",
    "We estimate Equation (1) by OLS and cluster the standard errors by workplace-occupation level.",
    "Pooled Difference-in-Differences."
  ]
}